sequenceDiagram
    participant Pod as Pod (db-backup)
    participant MDS as GKE Metadata Server<br/>169.254.169.254
    participant STS as GCP Security<br/>Token Service
    participant IAM as GCP IAM
    participant GCS as Cloud Storage

    Note over Pod: pg_dump completes,<br/>needs to upload to GCS

    Pod->>MDS: GET /computeMetadata/v1/<br/>instance/service-accounts/<br/>default/token

    Note over MDS: Checks pod's K8s SA: db-backup<br/>Reads annotation:<br/>iam.gke.io/gcp-service-account

    MDS->>STS: Exchange K8s identity<br/>project.svc.id.goog<br/>[feedforge/db-backup]

    STS->>IAM: Does feedforge-db-backup<br/>allow this K8s SA?

    Note over IAM: roles/iam.workloadIdentityUser<br/>granted to<br/>project.svc.id.goog<br/>[feedforge/db-backup]

    IAM-->>STS: Authorized

    STS-->>MDS: Short-lived GCP access token<br/>scoped to feedforge-db-backup

    MDS-->>Pod: {"access_token": "ya29.xxx..."}

    Pod->>GCS: PUT /upload/storage/v1/b/bucket/o<br/>Authorization: Bearer ya29.xxx...

    Note over GCS: feedforge-db-backup has<br/>storage.objectCreator<br/>on this bucket

    GCS-->>Pod: 200 OK

    Note over Pod: Backup uploaded
